---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Uses" description="The tools I use to make things.">
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Uses</h1>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-8">The tools I use to make things.</p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-10">Music Production</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-secondary">
      <li>Ableton Live 11</li>
      <li>Novation keypad</li>
      <li>Yamaha 88-key keyboard</li>
      <li>DDJ Rev 1 (DJing)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-10">Streaming/Content</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-secondary">
      <li>Rod Procaster (mic)</li>
      <li>Sony A6000 (camera)</li>
      <li>DJI Mic Mini</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-10">Development</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-secondary">
      <li>VS Code / Cursor</li>
      <li>Warp terminal</li>
      <li>GitHub</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-10">Making/Physical</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-secondary">
      <li>Woodworking tools</li>
      <li>Clay tools</li>
      <li>Skateboard setup</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-10">This Site</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-secondary">
      <li>Astro</li>
      <li>Bun</li>
      <li>Tailwind CSS</li>
      <li>Cloudflare Pages</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</Layout>
